{
  "texts": [
    "The JASC Code of 8530 pertaining to Reciprocating Engine Cylinder Section seems to fit the description given the keywords of Topic 3.",
    "With the limited information available in the MWOs, we can see why linking standardized maintenance codes to maintenance issues can be a tedious and difficult task.",
    "Even after preprocessing with TLP, we cannot provide a 100% linking of maintenance problems to the codes because we do not have any context of the issue other than the short phrases in the MWOs.",
    "Yet, our method with Topic Modeling is capable of identifying dominant topics and getting approximate matches to the maintenance codes with the closest descriptions.",
    "NLP has been very effective at analyzing text data from various domains."
  ]
}